<div style="position: relative; top: 25px; clear: both; "><div style="height: 64px; margin-bottom: 5px;">  <h2 style="float: right;">Fish</h2>  <img src="images/creatures/fish.gif"/></div><div style="margin-bottom: 35px; clear: both;">  <p>There are various types of Fish in Tibia. Ordinary Fish dwell in many lakes, ponds and of course Tibia's seas. They can be caught with a fishing rod or, once the ability of exploring the underwater worlds of Tibia has been acquired, be observed in their natural environment.</p>  <p>Fish have 25 hitpoints. They are immune to earth and fire damage. On the other hand, they are weak against energy and physical damage. It takes 0 mana to convince these creatures but they cannot be summoned. In addition, they are able to sense invisible creatures.</p>  <p>Fish yield 0 experience points. They carry nothing with them.</p>  </div></div>